HEADWORD: Sao
<hw>Sa"o</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any marine annelid of the genus <gen>Hyalinaecia</gen>, especially
<spn>Hyalinaecia tubicola</spn> of Europe, which inhabits a transparent
movable tube resembling a quill in color and texture.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

